and speed impact). While it is well known that motorcyclists frequently receive 
life threatening injuries to the head, spine and torso, this paper has been able 
to observe specific injury mechanisms such as pelvis impacts against the vehicle 
fuel tank and hyper-extension of the neck due to head impact on passenger cars.

